{"tid":108952,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"點解我原地跳起唔會俾地球一野甩去第二到","createTime":"2017-02-05T15:27:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-06T08:52:58.000Z","uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"879c7a5386ca608f5034ec43d54d6638f61533df","tid":108952,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T15:27:27.000Z","msg":"同埋地球自轉速度咁快，點解我地唔會覺得浪下浪下，想嘔咁<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n反而過山車，搭跑車咁慢速就會???"},{"pid":"34c2d074b1be599ce3b957f5d3ce84fdf5080bbb","tid":108952,"uid":3698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T15:54:48.000Z","msg":"邊有人坐車會嘔架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00b12a13c839cb8d1444904a709e58f51eef7d38","tid":108952,"uid":34517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T15:55:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>邊有人坐車會嘔架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n惺渣架"},{"pid":"7010964c184d4f9b6ce3efbc005f299296f094c6","tid":108952,"uid":6297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T15:56:45.000Z","msg":"係喎！唔講真係唔知"},{"pid":"37040253dac36c389dd6372ceae58221117f0e90","tid":108952,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T16:12:50.000Z","msg":"慣性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0f9a072d2e85fc9fe0bc2ea32eacd4c750d94b5","tid":108952,"uid":9677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T16:17:41.000Z","msg":"地心引力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76f6f13cdea6150447e268c29ac864f6d4d520cb","tid":108952,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T06:57:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>慣性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我地慣左咁撚高速<br />\n<br />\n點解坐個區區2，300km/hr既車就咁大離心力"},{"pid":"baa253110ed50a0a2bb8e6b51a252b2f14fff455","tid":108952,"uid":41243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T06:58:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>慣性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我地慣左咁撚高速<br />\n<br />\n點解坐個區區2，300km/hr既車就咁大離心力</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你中學有冇讀過phy"},{"pid":"d3cbfc429da8456ebe6fd760a6843b928ecc8350","tid":108952,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T07:01:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>慣性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我地慣左咁撚高速<br />\n<br />\n點解坐個區區2，300km/hr既車就咁大離心力</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你中學有冇讀過phy</blockquote><br />\n請解答下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c2eb1bd9d970b9e004c4621ea8e082ccc6ca628","tid":108952,"uid":67461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T07:07:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8e716bfe3680f3cebd4975be2af230bac1895a43","tid":108952,"uid":18605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T07:29:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>慣性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我地慣左咁撚高速<br />\n<br />\n點解坐個區區2，300km/hr既車就咁大離心力</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你中學有冇讀過phy</blockquote><br />\n請解答下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n慣左咁高速，但我地同地球係同步移動，所以地球自轉對我地嘅淨力係0<br />\n<br />\n由於我地同地球同步，姐係我地以地球自轉嘅速度移動緊<br />\n<br />\n當你跳起嘅時候，你就會繼續以地球速度前進，所以你唔會甩左去第二邊<br />\n<br />\n離心力唔係力，只係你個人嘅感覺，因為過山車衝落來嘅時候，你以接近自由落體嘅速度下跌，所以感到離心力"},{"pid":"415664e7a74e92d621be1795583533c6b19501f4","tid":108952,"uid":35347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T07:32:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>慣性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我地慣左咁撚高速<br />\n<br />\n點解坐個區區2，300km/hr既車就咁大離心力</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你中學有冇讀過phy</blockquote><br />\n請解答下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n慣左咁高速，但我地同地球係同步移動，所以地球自轉對我地嘅淨力係0<br />\n<br />\n由於我地同地球同步，姐係我地以地球自轉嘅速度移動緊<br />\n<br />\n當你跳起嘅時候，你就會繼續以地球速度前進，所以你唔會甩左去第二邊<br />\n<br />\n離心力唔係力，只係你個人嘅感覺，因為過山車衝落來嘅時候，你以接近自由落體嘅速度下跌，所以感到離心力</blockquote><br />\n就好似係一架直線行+冇改變速度嘅火車入面跳起咁<br />\n係會係返跳起個位落地"},{"pid":"97fa15dec65a4c78b0a77697486f8962d84b4306","tid":108952,"uid":41243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T08:52:58.000Z","msg":"其實如果認真答樓主, 其實係地球跳起, 落返去果陣係真係會移位<br />\n呢樣同勻速火車既情況唔同<br />\n因為地球自轉係non-inertial frame係有Coriolis force (一個pseduo force)"}]}